Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.89,0:00:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.85,0:00:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請往這邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近有一些和我們對立的惡魔來找我們麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.83,0:02:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您父親要我告訴你多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我先告退了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.55,0:02:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「體育節比賽項目 女子兩人三足比賽選手 佐伯玲子 嵩月 奏」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子若是想報名參加的話請舉手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小智不好了 我們的競爭相當激烈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 不做點什麼的話就
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小智 你知道洛高高中到處傳的那個被詛咒的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就是兩人三足比賽的隊友會招來不幸的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.25,0:03:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信不信由你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.76,0:03:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柱田老師到現在還是單身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近出勤變少了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.48,0:03:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為這個兩人三足比賽的詛咒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的 兩人三足的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 我不想被詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有候補選手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.66,0:03:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我們班的男生一點干勁都沒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 佐伯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小智一起去也可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人三足
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要是不想去的話也不用勉強的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我們要去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們出賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在干嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.79,0:04:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為他說什麼詛咒的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會遭什麼報應都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 妮婭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 出了這麼多事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.64,0:04:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你說的是姐姐的事情的話 已經沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道的東西有很多 現在不是沮喪的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼需要我們幫助的盡管說好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 要加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子 快點來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的和做的不一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.99,0:04:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:04:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須有誰參加的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我才會不畏懼那詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小智 你和嵩月一組
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來給玲子做領導
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小智 你臉紅什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該感謝我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 你們兩個一組啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.27,0:05:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏 是不是參加接力跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 作為田徑隊的一員要為參加運動會訓練呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 嵩月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好把帶子綁的緊一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為要是松了的話就輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.18,0:05:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍 稍微等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 夏目同學 把你的手放到我腰上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:05:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.28,0:06:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小智 快點快點摟住她的腰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再緊一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再緊點 要這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真淫荡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼重新開始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備 跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.49,0:06:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二一二一二…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H啊 H啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.71,0:06:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小智 再怎麼說你也離她太近了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 嵩月同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有辦法啊 因為是兩人三足比賽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真幸福啊 夏目智春
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵩月 腳…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 不快點解開的話會腫大的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:07:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是解不開這結…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 這個不剪掉恐怕不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你們到底打了多少個結啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先回教室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在這裡等玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二一二…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小智 我覺得你應該察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家可是看著你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算看見了也不要說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 都是因為我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嵩月你的錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對 都是因為小智他那邪惡的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子 快點來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.42,0:07:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你等那麼久不好意思啦 樋口同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為妹妹突然發燒不能來參加了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此 我來代替她訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.34,0:07:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准備完畢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你有什麼理由叫我哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.62,0:08:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.91,0:08:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你和我家玲子是那種關系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.66,0:08:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是 不是那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請你注意你的措辭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二一二…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一點點 加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膠水?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 完全粘住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個連鋸子也鋸不開的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個粘合力超強的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說有解開的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是明天才能送來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說在解開之前他們就一直要這樣粘在一起?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是嵩月你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但怎麼看都已成既定事實了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樋口所說的兩人三足的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋 對會長都做了些什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.99,0:09:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很無禮哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.51,0:09:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我拿出點氣勢 氣勢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二一二…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.12,0:09:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個累得夠嗆了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.69,0:09:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去保健室休息一下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.09,0:09:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師好像不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先找個地方坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.06,0:09:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 可以的話我想先把位置擦擦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:09:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.65,0:10:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就在那個窗簾的對面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誤會 只是誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須告訴兄長大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦 玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.04,0:10:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.61,0:10:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 樋口…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.38,0:10:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 他只是練習過猛了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說 這兩個人居然做那種不要臉的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.22,0:10:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目智春
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你的警告看來你是都當耳邊風了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 說了不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色狼 真差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是夏目君的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.78,0:10:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我想這樣做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵩月同學 你好像是引火上身了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.92,0:11:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 嵩月
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.38,0:11:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 還敢逃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~! 考拉生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考拉的憤怒是最厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮婭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 突然間跑出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.83,0:11:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會我再解釋 先幫我藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 考拉的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.23,0:11:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經誰都阻止不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.09,0:11:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是群搞不懂的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.69,0:11:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陶瓷刀都給搞斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.03,0:11:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃到這裡的話應該沒有問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 你是不想和嵩月同學分開才逃跑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:11:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵩月 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣綁在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的高中生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色狼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵩月才是 不累嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事 比起這個你的汗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小智啊 又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來怎麼不去洗澡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一天不洗還是可以的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是可以的話我還是想洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 嵩月同學好厲害 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.84,0:12:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好松軟 顏色好白哦 簡直像年糕一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:13:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.41,0:13:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 你從那裡開始洗嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 肯定是兩人三足的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樋口君 今天真是酣暢淋漓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功夫不負有心人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.12,0:13:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦 樋口君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒 肯定是兩人三足的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想和奏兩個人單獨睡一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 妮婭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上還是和嵩月同學倆人睡更好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.31,0:13:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.87,0:13:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個礙事的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知如此我就把你的運氣都吸掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.88,0:13:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少我要監視到小智不做奇怪的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:14:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明在洗澡的時候還在流鼻血
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡不著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵩月 你還醒著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.57,0:14:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳不痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.25,0:14:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以去陽台嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵醒他們倆不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二一二…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這樣真的不是很方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好明天休息
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那個解藥來之前就乖乖待在家裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:15:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話 明天我有個地方想去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我想去掃墓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是媽媽的祭日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽已經去世了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,0:15:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.84,0:15:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來我還真沒聽到你說起過你媽媽的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是會去那裡看她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親可能已經不記得她了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡魔使用魔力的話必須付出代價
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女性的惡魔會奪取所愛之人的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而男性的惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.52,0:15:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用魔力會耗盡所愛之人的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你的爸爸就是因為不斷使用魔力才…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親的記憶已經逐漸消逝了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以嵩月你才…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看到父親就會很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這個逐漸忘記了母親的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 要你陪我來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.88,0:16:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 難得休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家裡也很無聊的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.81,0:16:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家的時候解藥也可以拿到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是拿不到就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明很享受現在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個是嵩月組的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長 是小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:16:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去你父親那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有什麼想說的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.85,0:17:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去愛的人到底是怎麼樣的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心 是很強的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快躲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.47,0:17:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護社長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:17:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是惡魔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 奏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是找我的話在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我作對再等一百年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八伎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.81,0:18:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用管我 去戰斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.79,0:18:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小智 說得好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.67,0:18:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解決他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.02,0:18:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保護被母親愛著的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.47,0:19:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許對我的家人出手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.23,0:19:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越來越像你媽媽了啊 奏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你的戰斗 我就想起了你媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽生氣的時候也這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.59,0:20:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.03,0:20:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小智也從兩人三足中解脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算都解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:21:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好好想的話 奏的火焰不是能燒掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道也不想這麼做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.77,0:21:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是秘密…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小智
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.64,0:21:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直貴的墳墓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.52,0:23:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.47,0:23:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要隱藏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.28,0:23:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.34,0:23:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.35,0:23:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.99,0:23:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終究還是謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.22,0:23:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中糾結不已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.23,0:23:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終想傳達的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.66,0:23:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獻給你的真相

